<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-CHSA SMT High Current Inductor
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Characteristics
&lt;BR&gt; 
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Magnetically shielded rod core inductor
&lt;BR&gt; Operating temperature: -55°C to +150°C
&lt;BR&gt; Current capability up to 28A
&lt;BR&gt; Ideal coplanarity due to embedded solder pads
&lt;BR&gt; Automotive approved
&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt; Applications
&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Filter choke for motor electronics
&lt;BR&gt;Car infotainment
&lt;BR&gt;Multimedia applications
&lt;BR&gt;
&lt;BR&gt;
